/// \brief Handy helper to avoid longish comparisons.
///
/// The idea is taken from a talk from Bjrn Fahller at NDC TechTown 2019: Modern Techniques for Keeping Your Code DRY
/// (https://youtu.be/YUWuNpxZa5k)
/// \code
/// if( is{v}.any_of(A, B, C) ) { ... }
/// \endcode
